metadata.name: Drago the Legend
metadata.description:
OPI x Legendary Creature 

Since Dragons are often referred to as mystical than beast in asian countries , the east asian dragons most of the time has no wings.

The illustration depicts the beauty of lines and shapes. The black and white palette is used as it is used to depict the word "Balance".

Made using Photoshop

Size : 1920 x 1080
